title: Goldried Quintett
text:
The Goldried Quintett were an Austrian Volksmusik group from Matrei in Osttirol. The group was founded by Roland MÃ¼hlburger in 1980, and lasted until December 31, 2012 when the group disbanded. The Goldried quintet has achieved six gold, and two platinum records along with the Oberkrainer Award which was won in 2012.
